Generic single-database configuration.

## Migration chain

Alembic is the **single migration system** for RegEngine. The `migrations/`
directory of raw SQL files was removed after consolidation (April 2026).

To upgrade to the latest head:

    alembic upgrade head

Run `alembic history` to see the full chain.

## Admin service migrations (separate runner)

`services/admin/migrations/V1–V40` are managed **outside Alembic** by the
admin service's own migration runner. They will be merged into the main
Alembic chain during monolith consolidation (Phase 4).
